{
  "$resourceType": "tool",
  "name": "Medical Necessity Second Opinion",
  "description": "Call this tool when a claim's medical necessity assessment is ambiguous or uncertain. Specifically use this tool when: (1) one or more service lines have CPT/ICD-10 combinations that don't clearly align (e.g., a procedure code unrelated to the diagnosis), (2) the case involves complex multi-procedure surgical scenarios where standard rules don't clearly apply, or (3) you've already determined disposition is REVIEW but want a second opinion to validate or challenge your reasoning before finalizing. Send the relevant claim details and your initial assessment, and Claude will provide an independent medical-necessity perspective. Do NOT call this tool for routine claims with clear CPT/ICD-10 alignment or for claims that obviously fall under policy exclusions.",
  "location": "external",
  "type": "integration",
  "inputSchema": {
    "type": "object",
